    We take great pride in the quality of the food and service we provide. Our staff is friendly and welcoming, and we strive to make each visit to Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill an unforgettable experience. Come in and see us today and enjoy a great meal!

    Our Lunch Menu

    At Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill we are committed to providing our customers with a high-quality dining experience. Our menu offers a wide selection of steak cuts and sides that are sure to satisfy any craving. Our steaks are all made with the freshest ingredients and cooked to perfection. Additionally, our salad bar and signature sandwiches are sure to provide a delicious lunch option.

    VIEW LUNCH MENU

    Our Dinner Menu

    Welcome to Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill, where the finest steaks, salads, and seafood are served in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Our menu is carefully curated to provide you with the best flavors and the freshest ingredients. We are proud to serve prime-cut steaks, cooked to perfection and served with our signature sauces. We also offer a variety of salads, as well as seafood dishes that are sure to tantalize your taste buds. For an unforgettable dining experience, visit Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill.

    VIEW DINNER MENU

    Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill is an upscale steakhouse serving up all your favorite dishes. Our menu features a variety of steaks, seafood, pastas and more, all cooked to perfection. Our WEEKLY SPECIALS are always something to look forward to. Whether you're in the mood for steak, seafood, or something else, you'll find something delicious and unique to try. Stop by today and enjoy our friendly atmosphere and excellent service.

    Our Crafted Cocktails

    Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill is a modern steakhouse with a classic twist. Our hand-cut steaks are grilled to perfection and served with sides that will make your mouth water. For those looking for a unique dining experience, our craft cocktails are a must-try. Our signature cocktails are made with only the freshest ingredients and feature some of the best spirits in the world. Come in and try one today!
